<refentry id="package.versioncontrol.hg.container.versioncontrol-hg-container-repository.create">
 <refnamediv>
  <refname>
   <function>VersionControl_Hg_Container_Repository::create</function>
  </refname>
  <refpurpose>Create a repository</refpurpose>
 </refnamediv>
 <refsynopsisdiv>
  <funcsynopsis>
   <funcsynopsisinfo>require_once &apos;/Hg/Container/Repository.php&apos;;</funcsynopsisinfo>
   <funcprototype>
    <funcdef>
     <replaceable>
      <link linkend="package.versioncontrol.hg.container.versioncontrol-hg-container-repository-summary">
       <classname>VersionControl_Hg_Container_Repository</classname>
      </link>
     </replaceable>
     <function>VersionControl_Hg_Container_Repository::create</function>
    </funcdef>
    <paramdef>
     string
     <parameter>$path</parameter>
    </paramdef>
   </funcprototype>
  </funcsynopsis>
 </refsynopsisdiv>
 <refsect1 id="package.versioncontrol.hg.container.versioncontrol-hg-container-repository.create.desc">
  &title.desc;
  <para>
   This would make sense in only a very few isntances. For example, if a  programmer instantiated $hg without a path, and did this:
   <programlisting role="php">
<![CDATA[ $hg = new VersionControl_Hg();
 $repository = $hg->repository()->create('/path/to/repo');]]>
   </programlisting>
  </para>
  <para>However, its probably better to directly use the Init command, since  this create() function merely proxies it.</para>
 </refsect1>
 <refsect1 id="package.versioncontrol.hg.container.versioncontrol-hg-container-repository.create.param">
  &title.param;
  <para>
   <variablelist>
    <varlistentry>
     <term>
      &type.string;
      <parameter>$path</parameter>
     </term>
     <listitem>
      <para>
       The path at which to create a new Mercurial
       repository.
</para>
     </listitem>
    </varlistentry>
   </variablelist>
  </para>
 </refsect1>
 <refsect1 id="package.versioncontrol.hg.container.versioncontrol-hg-container-repository.create.throws">
  &title.throws;
  <para>
   <emphasis>throws</emphasis>
   no exceptions thrown
  </para>
 </refsect1>
 <refsect1 id="package.versioncontrol.hg.container.versioncontrol-hg-container-repository.create.note">
  &title.note;
